Package io.phrasefinder

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PhraseFinder
    Class PhraseFinder provides routines for querying the PhraseFinder web service.
    PhraseFinder.Options
    Options represents optional parameters that can be sent along with a query.
    PhraseFinder.Phrase
    Phrase represents a phrase, also called n-gram.
    PhraseFinder.Result
    Result represents a search result.
    PhraseFinder.Token
    Token represents a single token (word, punctuation mark, etc.) as part of a phrase.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PhraseFinder.Corpus
    Corpus is a numeric type that represents a corpus to be searched.
    PhraseFinder.Status
    Status is a type that reports whether a request was successful or not.
    PhraseFinder.Token.Tag
    TokenTag denotes the role of a token with respect to the query.
